[setpriv]
-------------
 * not using it to allow none root access
 * using it to restrict scope when executed by root
 * wont set cwd
 * wont clear environment
 * --reset-env - HOME SHELL USER LOGNAME PATH (PATH is currently wrong, set at compile time)
